en: Fish Pond was completed in 1940 as a class gift from the class of '38. It was refurbished by the class of 1977 in 1975. In 2011, Fish Pond was relocated across the street from its original location, placing it directly in front of Sbisa Dining Hall.
1939- Present; Gift of class of 1938; relocated 2011
